Enough;;2002;;PG-13;;Crime,Drama,Thriller;;5.8;;Michael Apted;;Jennifer Lopez,Billy Campbell,Tessa Allen,Juliette Lewis,Dan Futterman,Noah Wyle,Fred Ward,Christopher Maher,Janet Carroll,Bill Cobbs,Bruce A. Young,Bruce French,Ruben Madera,Dan Martin,Jeff Kober,Brent Sexton,Michael P. Byrne,Leif Riddell;;Local waitress Slim Miller discovers that the dream man she married isn't who she thought he was. Slim and her young daughter try to escape (aided by her previous boyfriend), but the now villainous husband pursues her relentlessly. Fearing also for the safety of her daughter, Slim decides that there's only one way out of the marriage: kill him.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0278435/